datasets.name: f3e09e49
datasets.query:
select 
*,
call_duration_in_sec/60 as call_duration_in_min
from
(
  select
    *
    from fins_genai.call_center.call_center_transcripts_analysis
)

datasets.name: 3067fd99
datasets.query:
select 
  sum(case when action_recommendation = 'apologize email' or action_recommendation = 'follow-up call' then 1 else 0 end) / count(*) as apologize_followup_ratio,
  sum(case when transcript not like 'all calls are recorded for training and monitoring purposes%' then 1 else 0 end)/count(*) as missing_intro_info,
  sum(case when transcript not like '%call us at 1-800-123-4567' then 1 else 0 end)/count(*) as missing_end_info,
  sum(case when sentiment = 'negative' then 1 else 0 end)/count(*) as negative_sentiment_ratio
from
(
  select
    *
    from fins_genai.call_center.call_center_transcripts_analysis
)

datasets.name: bd2441f9
datasets.query:
select 
  sum(no_inform_compliance)/count(*) as no_inform_compliance_ratio,
  sum(unprofessionalism)/count(*) as unprofessionalism_ratio,
  sum(no_identity_verification)/count(*) as no_identity_verification_ratio,
  sum(no_detail_explaination)/count(*) as no_detail_explaination_ratio,
  sum(no_inform_company_contact)/count(*) as no_inform_company_contact_ratio
from
(
  select
    *
    from fins_genai.call_center.call_center_transcripts_analysis
)
